{
  "text": "Based on the findings of the present work and previous studies, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] oxidative stress represents an important pathogenic factor in GO, at least in perpetuating ongoing reactions. However, because of limited cases in this study, more studies are warranted to provide additional information about the precise effect of 8-OHdG level on the natural history of the disease.",
